# Gringos homepage backdrop (locked)

## Fixed watermark

- `components/prologue/FixedBrandBackdrop.tsx` renders **one** full-viewport layer: `fixed`, below the nav (`top: var(--nav-h)`), `z-0`, `bg-charcoal`, faded `site-logo.webp` with **vmin** sizing so the **entire** mark stays visible.
- It stays **fixed** while the page scrolls; do not switch it to `absolute` inside a single section.

## Home shell

- `components/home/HomeView.tsx`: `<main className="relative">` then **`FixedBrandBackdrop` first**, then **`Hero`**. Order matters.
- **`Hero`**: keep **`relative z-10`** and **opaque** `bg-charcoal` + slides so the slideshow fully covers the fixed layer at the top.

## Section backgrounds (critical)

- **Do not** use opaque `bg-charcoal` or `bg-midnight` on stacked homepage sections — it **hides** the fixed logo and creates visible “blocks.”
- Use the **unified wash**: `relative z-10 bg-charcoal/45 backdrop-blur-sm` (same pattern on menu, locations, gallery, story, schedule, catering, social, popular).
- **Footer**: `bg-charcoal/70 backdrop-blur-md` (slightly stronger for legibility).
- **`FinalConversion`**: no navy / red **gradient slab**; same charcoal glass family as other bands.

## Locations card

- Truck **article**: `border-white/10`, **`bg-charcoal/35 backdrop-blur-md`** — **no** `from-navy/80` / gold ring “second skin” that reads as a different color block.
- **Hours** sub-panel: `bg-charcoal/30 backdrop-blur-sm` (not `bg-black/30`).

## Prologue

- `Prologue.tsx` is **copy only** (no duplicate logo). Welcome copy sits in a **glass** card (`bg-charcoal/35 backdrop-blur-md`, border) so it matches locations/menu; the section itself stays backdrop-clear above the fixed watermark.

When adding new homepage sections, match the **translucent charcoal + blur** pattern unless the section must be fully opaque (e.g. modals, nav, hero).
